divs: Sighting DetailsThe girlfriend was in the bedroom watching tv and asked me to come and look at something.There was a light in the sky that looked like a star but it went bright and dim repeatadly and it has green and red and white colors coming out of it.It appeared to move a very little ways and then it just sat there.It is still out there right now,and we first saw it about an hour ago.At first it just looks like a star.I guess i'm just saying that I know it aint just a star,and I don't know any aircraft that is just going to sit there.It is now 10:25 and it appears to have gone away.The girlfreind thinks that it looks like it is in the shape of a shield.The girlfreind said she thought it was a ufo right away because she has seen them previously.
Summary: looks something like a star but slightly larger and has colors coming out of it
